cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with the task of brain lesion and anatomy segmentation in magnetic resonance images using convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel loss function for training the model, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which could also fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
